{
  "$schema": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/code-yeongyu/oh-my-openagent/dev/assets/oh-my-opencode.schema.json",
  "agents": {
    "sisyphus": {
      "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6",
      "prompt_append": "## Automatic Session Reflection\n\nAt the end of every conversation — when the user's work is done and they signal they are finished (e.g. 'thanks', 'done', 'that's all', 'goodbye', closing remarks) — automatically offer to save a session reflection WITHOUT being asked.\n\nUse the `session-reflector` skill workflow:\n1. Draft a ≤30-line reflection covering: what was done, patterns noticed, corrections received, suggestions.\n2. Ask the user (via `question` tool): \"Save these learnings to `.agents/memory/pending/`? [y/n/edit]\"\n3. On y: write `{YYYY-MM-DD}-{slug}.md` to `.agents/memory/pending/`.\n4. On n or no closing signal detected: skip silently.\n\nDo NOT wait to be asked. Do NOT skip this because the session felt routine. Every session has learnings worth capturing."
    },
    "oracle": {
      "model": "anthropic/claude-opus-4-7"
    },
    "explore": {
      "model": "ollama-cloud/kimi-k2.5"
    },
    "multimodal-looker": {
      "model": "github-copilot/gemini-pro-3.1",
      "variant": "max"
    },
    "prometheus": {
      "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6"
    },
    "metis": {
      "model": "anthropic/claude-opus-4-7"
    },
